### Rust
debug/
target/
**/*.rs.bk
*.pdb

### Node
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# Runtime data
pids
*.pid
*.seed
*.pid.lock

# Compiled binary addons
build/Release

# Dependency directories
node_modules/

# TypeScript cache
*.tsbuildinfo

# npm caches / pack output
.npm
*.tgz

### Secrets
# The operator .env carries NPM_TOKEN and never enters git.
.env*
!.env.example

